
== Igishanga cya Nyandungu ==
mumyaka yashize uwumvaga [[Nyandungu Urban Wetland Eco-Tourism Park|nyandungu]] yayumvga nk'igishanga cyibasirwa nimyuzure igishanga giteye ubwoba<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ubukerarugendo/ahantu/article/igishanga-cya-nyandungu-kigiye-gushyirwamo-ubusitani-abantu-bajye-baharuhukira</ref>

kandi bamwe bagikoreshaga nk'ikimoteri kuko bamenagamo imyanda yo mungo zabo cyari igishanga ubonako

ntakerekezo gifite. muri icyogihe ibinyabuzima byari biri muri icyo gishanga harimo nk'inyoni nibindi byatangiye guhunga

utuyira nyabagendwa turasibama kubera imyuzure ikabije nisayo byamanurwaga nimvura ituruka hirya nohino muri [[Kigali]].

hakorerwaga kandi ubuhinzi butita kubidukikije ikigishanga cyari cyarakamye kubera kutitabwaho no gucukuramo ibumba<ref>https://panorama.rw/index.php/2021/11/11/rema-icyanya-cya-nyandungu-kizatangira-gukora-mu-kuboza/</ref>

== Ubukungu ==
mu mwaka wa 2015 nibwo hatekerejwe umushinga wabyazwa muri iki gishanga murwego rwo kubungabunga ibidukikije<ref>http://thesourcepost.com/index.php/2021/11/04/dutembere-mu-gishanga-cya-nyandungu-ahantu-nyaburanga-habungabunga-ibidukikije/</ref>

ndetse no kukibyaza umusaruro kigakurura ba mukerarugendo basura [[Umujyi wa Kigali|umujyi wa kigali]] aribwo hafatwaga ingamba zo kugihinduramo

[[Pariki|pariki y'ubukerarugendo]] bubungabunga ibidukikije ikongewa muzari zisanzwemu [[Rwanda]]. imirimo yo kugitunganya yatangiye muri 2016

== Akamaro ==
muguhindura iki gishanga hatekerejwe kubungabunga urusobe rw'[[Ibinyabuzima n'inyamaswa byo mu Rwanda|ibinyabuzima]],kubakamo ibikorwa remezo ndetse no kubibyaza<ref>https://igihe.com/ubukerarugendo/ahantu-nyaburanga/article/nyandungu-yabaye-nshya-igishanga-cyarasazuwe-kigiye-gukoreshwa-nka-pariki-yo</ref>

umusaruro bigakurura ba [[Ubukerarugendo mu Rwanda|Mukerarugendo]] mu [[Rwanda]] iki gishanga kandi hateganyijwe guterwamo ibiti bisa nkibiri  gucika birimo

‘umugote’, ‘igikakarubamba’, ‘imiravumba’, ‘iminyinya’, ‘ikirogora’, ‘umubirizi’, ‘igicuncu’, ‘igitenetene’, ‘umukunde

kugirango bizifashshwe mugusobanurira abakiri bato ibyo aribyo hari kandi ubusitani bwo kwicaramo ndetse nutuyira twa siporo

turi kubuso bwa kirometero 10 hatewemo kandi imiti imwe nimwe yo mubimera yakoreshwaga nabakera mubuvuzi gakondo

nyuma yo gutunganwya kwiki Gishanga kandi byatumye bimwe mubinyabuzima byari byarahunze birimo nk'inyoni nibindi.<ref>https://www.isangostar.rw/ibyegeranyo/tuhamenye/article/tuhamenye-nyandungu-wetland-eco</ref>

== Inyungu Rusange ==
iki gishanga gifitiye igihugu akamaro cyane cyane [[Umujyi wa Kigali|umujyi wa kigali]] ndetse nabagituriye kuko kigizwe nurusobe rw '[[Ibinyabuzima n'inyamaswa byo mu Rwanda|ibinyabuzima]]<ref>https://panorama.rw/index.php/2021/11/11/rema-icyanya-cya-nyandungu-kizatangira-gukora-mu-kuboza/</ref>

ndetse nibyatsi bitanga imiti myinshi itandukanye yifashishwa mukuvura [[Indwara y’igisebe cy’umufunzo|indwara]] zimwe nazimwe ikigishanga kirimo kandi

ahantu ho kuruhukira,aho gufatira amafunguro,aho gukinira ikinamico,ndetse nutuyira twa siporo zabanyamaguru ndetse namagare<ref>http://www.fonerwa.org/kin/kubungabunga-igishanga-cya-nyundungu-ndetse-no-kubakamo-pariki-yubukerarugendo</ref>

== Inyoni ziri muri iki gishanga ==
muri ikigishanga harimo amoko y'inyoni asaga 70 ndetse nurusobe rw'ibinyabuzima

bitandukanye namoko y'ibiti menshi atandukanye harimo natanga imiti.

